document_data.name: Harrowdale Harbor
document_data.mainbody: '''Harrowdale Harbor''' was found in the town of [[New Velar|Harrowdale]] on the [[Dragon Reach]].
document_data.Description: The harbor had two named piers, the [[Heart of the Harbor]] and [[Harrow Plow Pier]], and another unnamed pier on its north side at the end of [[Lancegallop Lane]]. Several trading warehouses and offices were located on the harbor including the [[Shaleel Warehouses]], [[Treskeden House]], and [[Harrowcoaster House]].
